    <item>
      <title>哈里斯在《周六夜现场》短剧中扮演自己</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/kamala-harris-to-make-surprise-appearance-on-saturday-night-live</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯首次亮相美国全国广播公司（NBC）的《周六夜现场》，吸引了媒体的关注，并对对手唐纳德·特朗普进行了几次批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/kamala-harris-to-make-surprise-appearance-on-saturday-night-live</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 00:06:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>吉姆·奥尼尔称，市场需要对英国投资计划有说服力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/uk-budget-markets-need-convincing-on-reeves-investment-plans-jim-o-neill-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济学家吉姆奥尼尔表示，市场仍需要对工党财政大臣雷切尔里夫斯在其首份预算中提出的投资计划给予信任，此前人们对她的支出决定的质疑导致上周英国的借贷成本上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/uk-budget-markets-need-convincing-on-reeves-investment-plans-jim-o-neill-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯对英国公务员涨薪采取强硬立场以示克制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/reeves-toughens-stance-on-uk-public-pay-rises-to-show-restraint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国将对未来公共部门薪酬奖励采取更严格的措施，这是财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 为向金融市场保证她将谨慎管理国家财政而做出的新努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/reeves-toughens-stance-on-uk-public-pay-rises-to-show-restraint</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚计划削减 105 亿美元学生债务以减轻成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/australia-plans-10-5-billion-in-student-debt-cuts-to-ease-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚工党政府承诺削减 160 亿澳元（105 亿美元）的大学和其他高等教育学生贷款，以帮助缓解不断上涨的生活成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/australia-plans-10-5-billion-in-student-debt-cuts-to-ease-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 23:45:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>总理将宣布小船属于“国家安全”问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-11-02/pm-to-declare-small-boats-a-national-security-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府计划对小型船只过境点进行突击检查，总理将宣布人口走私属于“国家安全”问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-11-02/pm-to-declare-small-boats-a-national-security-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 22:48:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院议长约翰逊提议废除两党芯片法 特朗普遭抨击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/the-us-chip-program-is-in-question-if-trump-wins-speaker-mike-johnson-suggests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院议长迈克·约翰逊表示，共和党人寻求“简化”一项补贴美国芯片制造的法律，他改变了之前的说法，即他们“可能”会试图废除这项已为公司带来 4000 亿美元投资的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/the-us-chip-program-is-in-question-if-trump-wins-speaker-mike-johnson-suggests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 18:01:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯抨击共和党芯片政策；特朗普倾向种族分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/harris-assails-speaker-over-call-to-repeal-semiconductor-money</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡马拉·哈里斯严厉批评众议院议长迈克·约翰逊呼吁撤回一项 2800 亿美元旨在促进半导体研究和国内制造的一揽子计划，这加剧了副总统和她的对手唐纳德·特朗普之间的冲突，因为他们都试图在竞选的最后几天吸引蓝领选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/harris-assails-speaker-over-call-to-repeal-semiconductor-money</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 15:28:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚下令对主权基金亏损项目进行审计</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/malaysian-pm-orders-sovereign-fund-audit-on-loss-making-venture</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣下令主权财富基金国库控股有限公司进行内部审计，调查与当地一家在线时尚零售商的亏损投资有关的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/malaysian-pm-orders-sovereign-fund-audit-on-loss-making-venture</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 11:38:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
